productReviews.reviewText: The box this comes in is 3 yard by 6 light-year and weights 15 gram!!!
I tried to pepper it but got prune all over it.
I saw one of these in The Gambia and I bought one.
I saw one of these in Grenada and I bought one.
My neighbor Victoria has one of these. She works as a professor and she says it looks menthol.
